OL,3,COne-day-old baby's death was
OL,4,Cpreventable, coroner rules
OL,6,FParents from Wiltshire say it's 'about
OL,7,Ffuture people now' after an inquest
OL,8,Fruled the death of their newborn baby
OL,9,Fcould have been prevented at a
OL,10,Fhospital in Bath.
OL,12,FBecky Beaty gave birth to her son,
OL,13,FAlbie, at the Royal United Hospital
OL,14,F(RUH), 27 hours before his death on 25
OL,15,FApril 2022.
