OL,3,COne-day-old baby's death was
OL,4,Cpreventable, coroner rules
OL,6,FAfter driving 20 minutes away from the
OL,7,Fhospital, Albie stopped breathing on
OL,8,Ftheir way home to Westbury. Becky and
OL,9,Fhis father, Jack, spent 57 minutes
OL,10,Fgiving their newborn CPR while waiting
OL,11,Ffor an ambulance.
OL,13,FBecky says Albie passed away "in the
OL,14,Fback of the car" on their way home.
OL,15,FShe said: "Jack called 999, I started
OL,16,FCPR in the backseat, and it took 57
OL,17,Fminutes for the ambulance to arrive
OL,18,Fbecause they couldn't get our
OL,19,Flocation, which we've now learnt
OL,20,Fbecause it was the call handler's
OL,21,Ffirst day without someone beside her."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
