OL,3,COne-day-old baby's death was
OL,4,Cpreventable, coroner rules
OL,6,FInvestigations found that Albie died
OL,7,Fof a collapsed lung, known as
OL,8,Fpneumothorax, in which a coroner ruled
OL,9,Fthat he "would still be alive had he
OL,10,Freceived the care he should have had".
OL,12,FThe five-day inquest last month found
OL,13,Fthat Albie had difficulty breathing
OL,14,Ffor 24 hours, during which
OL,15,Fobservations should have been made.
OL,17,FMother-of-four Becky says she 'paid
OL,18,Fthe ultimate price' after listening to
OL,19,Fassurances from her midwife that Albie
OL,20,Fwas healthy.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
