OL,3,COne-day-old baby's death was
OL,4,Cpreventable, coroner rules
OL,6,FShe added: "I raised concerns, and the
OL,7,Fmidwife said they were keeping an eye.
OL,8,FI feel like I did all I could have
OL,9,Fdone. I was constantly getting
OL,10,Freassured that it's normal.
OL,12,F"It was simple, just to do
OL,13,Fobservations. Obviously, we're angry;
OL,14,Fit's a natural thing to feel angry. I
OL,15,Fjust hope they do better and don't do
OL,16,Fit again.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
