OL,3,COne-day-old baby's death was
OL,4,Cpreventable, coroner rules
OL,6,F"It's not a rare condition. It is
OL,7,Ftreatable, easily treatable, from my
OL,8,Funderstanding. You just need to be
OL,9,Fquick to recognise the signs, and the
OL,10,Fsigns were there."
OL,12,FAlbie's parents say they want to make
OL,13,Fsure the 'preventable failings' do not
OL,14,Fhappen to other families
OL,16,FSpeaking about the impact it's had on
OL,17,Ftheir family, Jack says he "couldn't
OL,18,Fsettle" back into his life.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
