OL,6,FHe said: "I had a job at the time, I
OL,7,Fwas an estate agent locally. Trying to
OL,8,Fgo back to work after - I couldn't. I
OL,9,Fhad a few different jobs to keep a
OL,10,Froof over our heads. There's no help;
OL,11,Fthe bills don't go away. You've just
OL,12,Fgot to carry on."
OL,14,F"I'm looking forward to working with
OL,15,FRUH and the South West Ambulance
OL,16,FService and putting things behind
OL,17,Fus... It's not about us now, it's
OL,18,Fabout the next people."
