OL,4,Cpreventable, coroner rules
OL,6,FRoyal United Hospitals Bath NHS
OL,7,FFoundation Trust says it's implemented
OL,8,F"significant steps" to "improve the
OL,9,Fcare" of newborns. These include
OL,10,Fmonitoring the amount of oxygen in
OL,11,Ftheir blood as standard practice and
OL,12,Fbetter staff training.
OL,14,FA new process called the 'Newborn
OL,15,FEarly Warning Trigger and Track' tool
OL,16,Fhas also been introduced, which
OL,17,Finvolves listening to and acting on
OL,18,Fparents' concerns.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
