OL,3,COne-day-old baby's death was
OL,4,Cpreventable, coroner rules
OL,6,FIn a statement, a spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"We are truly sorry that Albie did not
OL,8,Freceive the highest standards of care
OL,9,Fwhen he was in our hospital, and we
OL,10,Fextend our heartfelt condolences to
OL,11,FAlbie's family for their devastating
OL,12,Floss.
OL,14,F"The loss of Albie has been deeply
OL,15,Fdistressing for his parents and loved
OL,16,Fones, and our thoughts remain with
OL,17,Fthem."
