OL,6,FA spokesperson for the South Western
OL,7,FAmbulance Service NHS Foundation Trust
OL,8,Fsays, "We would again like to offer
OL,9,Four sincere apologies and condolences"
OL,10,Fto Albie's family.
OL,12,F"Our Emergency Medical Dispatchers
OL,13,F(EMDs) complete comprehensive training
OL,14,Fand need to successfully achieve the
OL,15,Frequired standard before they enter
OL,16,Fthe 'live' environment of answering
OL,17,F999 calls.
